{"tid":1556746,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香城Online新副本]定期主題式文宣/討論","createTime":"2019-09-10T00:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T03:09:26.000Z","uid":37722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2e0731358d441823025af7c619113615b297fd83","tid":1556746,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:34:57.000Z","msg":"大家有冇發現而家文宣, 討論嘅焦點開始有d模糊化, 因為每日新聞太多, 所以一d好恐怖噁心嘅警暴post都沉哂.<br />\n<br />\n既然而家抗爭到左樽頸位, 而且開始有人認同要重塑連儂牆, 我地就需要有個<span style=\"color: red;\">系統性討論及宣傳策略, 等我地唔好忘記未解決嘅嚴重事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n既然犬隻記者/政府每個星期都有唔同主題, 我建議我地又黎個每星期宣傳/討論主題, 方式如下:<br />\n<br />\n1. 係個段時間期間, 文宣, 連儂牆, 推文語句都要係同主題有關 eg 推文語: 新屋嶺濫暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 每星期/定期作討論主題更新, 而且主題可以來回更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 每次主題應該要針對極嚴重嘅深層次問題, 而非單一事件 eg 新屋嶺男女受辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n, 某晚警犬放tg清場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 有重大嚴重事件發生嘅話, 主題立即更新, 所有討論焦點相應改變, <span style=\"color: red;\">但如果發現風向有異就轉返去原來戰線</span><br />\n<br />\n大家都明個玩法就而家開始啦, 方式可以討論, 但請湧躍參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今星期主題: 新屋嶺濫暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nReference:<br />\n女手足被裸搜凌辱:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tHw7z_bP9Co\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtHw7z_bP9Co&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNnejezXkYyU2Z26LisGJHUw%3D&h=7b7dedac\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tHw7z_bP9Co</a><br />\n<br />\n再有裸搜女揭警性暴 轟警捏造記事冊：見到私處先放過我<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1516854/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1516854/page/1</a><br 